  "texts": [
    "However, students might tend to rely on AI if its role is not planned properly (Darvishi et al., 2024).",
    "Therefore, it may be crucial to implement strategic instructional and pedagogical interventions for effective use of AI tools for learning purposes.",
    "Effective AI integration may involve embedding AI into the curriculum in a way that complements traditional teaching methods and supports students' learning (Sun et al., 2024; Tan et al., 2024).",
    "This can be achieved through concurrent instructor assistance and guidance (Darvishi et al., 2024; Paiva and Bittencourt, 2020).",
    "Incorporating AI into collaborative learning activities can also enhance peer-to-peer learning, as students can collectively refine their problem-solving approaches with AI support (Rasul et al., 2023; Suciati et al., 2024)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
